{"tid":674112,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"驚 錢 七 衝 馬 路　錢 嘉 樂 當 眾 喝 湯 盈 盈","createTime":"2018-05-22T12:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T10:05:38.000Z","uid":35964,"like":17,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"882d9ff0283be64809786f321f4fb6f128298115","tid":674112,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:05:01.000Z","msg":"湯盈盈與錢嘉樂在2012年結婚，婚後誕下大女錢凱晴（Alyssa）和細女錢凱琪（Kassidy），一家四口過着幸福生活。錢嘉樂的電影工作一部接一部，湯盈盈一度減少幕前工作，專心相夫教女，直到近期才復出拍劇，不過他們沒有因此忽略家庭，依然爭取時間陪囡囡，是圈中出名的恩愛夫妻。<br />\n<br />\n拖細女行先<br />\n不過日前有《蘋果》讀者李小姐透過「爆相爆片」，表示目睹錢嘉樂當街大聲話老婆！李小姐表示在母親節當日下午3時左右，湯盈盈和錢嘉樂帶着兩名囡囡行經賽西湖公園外，李小姐聽到他們很大聲說話，還覺得表現有點𤷪𤺧;。李小姐說：「嗰陣我喺對面馬路，最初聽到湯盈盈話『拖住個女，小心佢走出馬路』，跟住錢嘉樂就好大聲話『咁你交畀我喇，唔好咁多嘢講！』跟住就拖住細女向前行，同拖住大女嘅湯盈盈隔咗一段好遠嘅距離。」<br />\n湯盈盈接受傳媒訪問，否認被老公錢嘉樂大聲話：「嗰日我哋玩得好開心，係開心家庭日，係咪當時細路做危險動作，佢緊張咋？」她又笑說：「嘉樂話佢平時唔緊張，唔知係咪你哋睇住啦。」<br />\n<br />\n「開心家庭日」<br />\n原來當日湯盈盈一家四口之後去了公園玩，問到母親節慶祝活動，湯盈盈說：「嗰晚我哋一家約咗奶奶同埋鍾麗淇一家食飯慶祝，我哋仲訂咗花畀媽媽同奶奶，又同兩個女一齊包禮物送畀工人姐姐，始終對方都係人哋媽媽，放下自己嘅小朋友去照顧自己個女。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180516/large/16ec2p1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180516%2Flarge%2F16ec2p1e.jpg&h=7c28dd2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n湯盈盈指母親節當日一家人玩得好開心，更去了公園。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180516/large/16ec2p2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180516%2Flarge%2F16ec2p2e.jpg&h=45a5e1ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n錢嘉樂被目睹話完老婆湯盈盈後，一手拖着細女行先。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180516/large/1526392299_a869.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180516%2Flarge%2F1526392299_a869.jpg&h=5a9e4dd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n湯盈盈當晚相約鍾麗淇一起吃飯慶祝母親節。"},{"pid":"1155dabf4ae2569effe3cd6bad66c373dacfc07d","tid":674112,"uid":41204,"like":7,"dislike":28,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"物以類聚"},{"pid":"d56109a79b8ce3d207c75259bf5910c4b57ce14b","tid":674112,"uid":153679,"like":438,"dislike":11,"score":427,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:08:58.000Z","msg":"鍾麗淇個女係......"},{"pid":"aa8cd2b68b3d42078f2a107ba6abce96db3fdcf6","tid":674112,"uid":132587,"like":377,"dislike":40,"score":337,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:09:15.000Z","msg":"鍾麗淇個女係咪同thanos生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812efb142f2658b5c5eee046e8330e8ea7a562db","tid":674112,"uid":29093,"like":201,"dislike":2,"score":199,"quote":{"pid":"d56109a79b8ce3d207c75259bf5910c4b57ce14b","tid":674112,"uid":153679,"like":438,"dislike":11,"score":427,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:08:58.000Z","msg":"鍾麗淇個女係......"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:09:55.000Z","msg":"有病既小女孩"},{"pid":"a69fdbbe875e81c62f3fcd6a6a6726f4813aeff3","tid":674112,"uid":69886,"like":9,"dislike":346,"score":-337,"quote":{"pid":"d56109a79b8ce3d207c75259bf5910c4b57ce14b","tid":674112,"uid":153679,"like":438,"dislike":11,"score":427,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:08:58.000Z","msg":"鍾麗淇個女係......"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"發現外太空生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f471ee8c62978717ad649d36edd92573e899fda1","tid":674112,"uid":66254,"like":643,"dislike":4,"score":639,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:10:30.000Z","msg":"錢嘉樂當眾喝湯"},{"pid":"eab88ef08e63fa5c0bfe98f301bb31be54473e77","tid":674112,"uid":46910,"like":15,"dislike":120,"score":-105,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:11:36.000Z","msg":"做咩成班生曬異形<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f847ea54a7305af8776a6ba7d0f283509ce5fb","tid":674112,"uid":810,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:13:07.000Z"